"``--profile``. Combine com o override de CPU, se necessĂˇrio:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/using_docker_compose.rst:166
msgid ""
"The private index is also published on the host (default port ``8080``), "
"so other machines on the same network can reuse it with ``pip install -i "
"http://<host>:8080/simple ...``."
msgstr ""
"O Ă­ndice privado tambĂ©m Ă© publicado no host (porta padrĂŁo ``8080``), de "
"modo que outras mĂˇquinas na mesma rede podem reutilizĂˇ-lo com ``pip "
"install -i http://<host>:8080/simple ...``."

#: ../../source/getting_started/using_docker_compose.rst:171
msgid ""
"When launching models with the **vLLM** or **SGLang** engines, Xinference"
" by default resolves some dependencies from hardcoded public indexes "
"(``wheels.vllm.ai``, ``download.pytorch.org``). The offline ``pip.conf`` "
"above overrides them with the private index, which means those wheels "
"must be present in ``./wheels`` â€” mirror the required ``vllm`` / "
"``torch`` CUDA wheels when preparing Step 1. Alternatively, set "
"``XINFERENCE_ENABLE_VIRTUAL_ENV=0`` in ``offline.env`` to skip runtime "
"installs entirely and rely on the packages baked into the image."
msgstr ""
"Ao inicializar modelos com os mecanismos **vLLM** ou **SGLang**, o "
"Xinference, por padrĂŁo, resolve algumas dependĂŞncias a partir de Ă­ndices "
"pĂşblicos fixos no cĂłdigo (``wheels.vllm.ai``, ``download.pytorch.org``). "
"O ``pip.conf`` offline acima os sobrescreve com o Ă­ndice privado, o que "
"significa que esses wheels devem estar presentes em ``./wheels`` â€” "
"espelhe os wheels CUDA de ``vllm`` / ``torch`` necessĂˇrios ao preparar o "
"Passo 1. Como alternativa, defina ``XINFERENCE_ENABLE_VIRTUAL_ENV=0`` em "
"``offline.env`` para pular completamente as instalaĂ§Ăµes em tempo de "
"execuĂ§ĂŁo e depender dos pacotes jĂˇ incluĂ­dos na imagem."

#: ../../source/getting_started/using_docker_compose.rst:180
msgid "Offline model weights"
msgstr "Pesos de modelos offline"

#: ../../source/getting_started/using_docker_compose.rst:181
msgid ""
"The offline configuration sets ``HF_HUB_OFFLINE=1`` and "
"``TRANSFORMERS_OFFLINE=1``, so model weights are read from the local "
"cache only. Populate the cache before going offline, either by pointing "
"the cache variables in ``.env`` at host directories that already contain "
"the models, or by launching each model once on a connected host and "
"copying the volumes. Models can also be loaded from arbitrary local paths"
" by registering custom models or passing ``--model-path``."
msgstr ""
"A configuraĂ§ĂŁo offline define ``HF_HUB_OFFLINE=1`` e "
"``TRANSFORMERS_OFFLINE=1``, portanto os pesos dos modelos sĂŁo lidos "
"apenas do cache local. Popule o cache antes de ficar offline, seja "
"apontando as variĂˇveis de cache no ``.env`` para diretĂłrios do host que "
"jĂˇ contenham os modelos, seja inicializando cada modelo uma vez em um "
"host conectado e copiando os volumes. Os modelos tambĂ©m podem ser "
"carregados de caminhos locais arbitrĂˇrios registrando modelos "
"personalizados ou passando ``--model-path``."

#: ../../source/getting_started/using_docker_compose.rst:188
msgid "Enforced network isolation (optional)"
msgstr "Isolamento de rede reforĂ§ado (opcional)"

#: ../../source/getting_started/using_docker_compose.rst:189
msgid ""
"The offline configuration redirects every download to local sources, but "
"by itself it does not prevent the containers from reaching the Internet "
"if the host happens to have connectivity. To *guarantee* isolation at the"
" network level, add the air-gap override, which moves Xinference and the "
"private PyPI server onto an ``internal`` Docker network with no external "
"routing:"
msgstr ""
"A configuraĂ§ĂŁo offline redireciona todos os downloads para fontes locais,"
" mas, por si sĂł, nĂŁo impede que os contĂŞineres alcancem a Internet caso o"
" host tenha conectividade. Para *garantir* o isolamento no nĂ­vel de rede,"
" adicione o override de air gap, que move o Xinference e o servidor PyPI "
"privado para uma rede Docker ``internal`` sem roteamento externo:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/using_docker_compose.rst:199
msgid ""
"Because Docker does not publish ports of internal-only networks, the "
"override adds a minimal TCP gateway (``alpine/socat``) that forwards the "
"API port from the host into the isolated network. The gateway only relays"
" inbound traffic to ``xinference:9997``; the containers cannot use it as "
"an egress path. Remember to transfer the ``alpine/socat`` image to the "
"offline host along with the others."
msgstr ""
"Como o Docker nĂŁo publica portas de redes somente internas, o override "
"adiciona um gateway TCP mĂ­nimo (``alpine/socat``) que encaminha a porta "
"da API do host para a rede isolada. O gateway apenas retransmite o "
"trĂˇfego de entrada para ``xinference:9997``; os contĂŞineres nĂŁo podem "
"usĂˇ-lo como caminho de saĂ­da. Lembre-se de transferir a imagem "
"``alpine/socat`` para o host offline junto com as demais."

#: ../../source/getting_started/using_docker_compose.rst:207
msgid ""
"In this mode the private PyPI server is not published on the host; it is "
"only reachable from containers inside the isolated network. Verify the "
"isolation from within the container â€” external requests must fail while "
"the private index stays reachable:"
msgstr ""
"Nesse modo, o servidor PyPI privado nĂŁo Ă© publicado no host; ele sĂł pode "
"ser alcanĂ§ado por contĂŞineres dentro da rede isolada. Verifique o "
"isolamento de dentro do contĂŞiner â€” as requisiĂ§Ăµes externas devem falhar "
"enquanto o Ă­ndice privado permanece acessĂ­vel:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/using_docker_compose.rst:219
